The purpose of this framework is to provide users with a very lightweight and quick way to get small to mid size applications up and running.  It also will be very flexible and customizable.  We want Users to be able to do things their way if they want, but we will provide best practices and guidelines.  This will be a base framework for getting projects done quickly.  It will provide the essential pieces to what is required in most small to mid size applications.  It will also be easy for users to plug in third party applications and integrate them into their app seamlessly.